Ben Sunderman, 19, who has Down syndrome was accepted for a special education internship with Embassy Suites . 
  He was one of 12 students with special needs to get the internship which will begin in August . 
  He has a list of things to do before turning 21 that includes getting a job . 
  On April 10 he watched a video of himself reading his acceptance letter and shouting 'I get the job!'